Cook pasta according to package directions; drain. Meanwhile, cook sausage and onion in large non-stick skillet until sausage is lightly browned. Drain if needed. Add peppers; cook 2 minutes, stirring frequently. Add tomato sauce and oregano. Bring to a boil. Reduce heat; simmer, uncovered, 5 minutes. Stir in pasta and toss with Parmesan cheese.